# Legacy cluster launchers wrote host-specific logs beside the repository.
# Keep them in place without making the sealed-audit worktree appear dirty.
/*.out
/*.pid
/*.meta

# Regenerable figure/selector outputs that were dirtying the cluster worktree
# and blocking enqueue_table12.sh's clean-tree guard. The tracked figure
# artifacts (fig6_evidence_chain_generated.tex, fig2_evidence_chain_data.json)
# are NOT matched by these patterns; only the conceptual/preview scratch and
# ad-hoc selector verdict dumps are.
.ipynb_checkpoints/
docs/figures/fig2_concept_*
docs/figures/fig2_profile_*
figures/*_concept.tex
/*_verdict.json
